      <div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-[var(--color-text-primary)] group-hover:text-[var(--color-accent)] mb-1">Open Portable Entitlement (OPE)</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-secondary)] mb-3">A portable entitlement layer for gated content. Subscribe once, read anywhere.</p>
